If you are tight on a disk space and would not like to keep the .rar file around, you can switch to the .html version torrent and then delete the .rar file.

Here is how to do it:
1) Download the following torrent file first:
http://antimatrix.org/Convert/torrents/NWO_ZioNazi_Illuminati_Secret_Societies_Vol_4.torrent

2) no need to download the files. Just change the directory to point to where you extracted the files from RAR. In uTorrent do:
Advanced -> Set download location.
The do Advanced -> Force recheck

3) You should get 100% of files after force recheck.

4) Then you can start seeding the HTML version of torrent and delete your .rar file.

The advantage of the HTML version is that you can start reading some stuff before you complete downloading the whole torrent.
You just need to get the css, img, and Images subdirectories first so your style look good and all the pictures show up.
You do this by setting priority to High on files in those subdirectories, and, once you got all the .css files and images, if you care about images,
you can set download priority to High to those books that you want to read while downloading the whole thing.
